large训练：
conda activate simvla
cd /home/hg731/HG/SimVLA

export PYTHONNOUSERSITE=1
export CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=0
export NUM_PROCESSES=1
export GRADIENT_ACCUMULATION_STEPS=1
export SMOLVLM_MODEL=./pretrained/SmolVLM-500M-Instruct
export VLM_TORCH_DTYPE=float32

bash train_smolvlm_large.sh 32 0.1 ./runs/simvla_libero_all_large


small训练：
conda activate simvla
cd /home/hg731/HG/SimVLA

export PYTHONNOUSERSITE=1
export CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=0
export NUM_PROCESSES=1
export NUM_WORKERS=8
export GRADIENT_ACCUMULATION_STEPS=1
export SMOLVLM_MODEL=./pretrained/SmolVLM-500M-Instruct
export VLM_TORCH_DTYPE=float32
export LOG_INTERVAL=100
export LEARNING_RATE=1e-5

bash train_smolvlm_small.sh 32 0.1 ./runs/simvla_libero_all_small

参数含义：

4：每个 GPU / process 的 batch size。A6000 这种 48G 可以先试 32；OOM 就降到 16 或 8。
0.1：VLM backbone 的学习率系数，实际 VLM LR = 2e-4 * 0.1 = 2e-5。
./runs/simvla_libero_all_large：输出目录。
large 脚本默认：hidden_size=1024、depth=24、num_heads=16、iters=200000、num_actions=10、image_size=384。


断点续训：
export ITERS=400000
bash train_smolvlm_large.sh 32 0.1 ./runs/simvla_libero_all_small ./runs/simvla_libero_all_small/ckpt-200000
